    bibo:volume "4820" ;
    dc:creator "Fouquet, Antoine; Jairam, Rawien; Ouboter, Paul; Kok, Philippe J. R." ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Two new species of Anomaloglossus (Anura: Aromobatidae) of the stepheni group from Suriname" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397449>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397451>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397445>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397447> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397449>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Spectrograms and oscillograms of the advertisement calls of the two species described herein, Anomaloglossus saramaka sp. nov. and A. vacheri sp. nov., along with the calls of four additional described species of the A. stepheni group; in a 2 s time window (top) and a close-up in a 0.1 s time window (bottom)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4397449/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397451>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. The tadpole of Anomaloglossus saramaka sp. nov. and A. vacheri sp. nov., and pictures of habitat and males in situ. Top: ventral and lateral view of AF3865_B at Gosner stage 29, a close-up of the mouth, a male (MNHN_RA_2019.0029, field n°AF3897) carrying 9 tadpoles (note the shredding skin), and habitat where males deposit tadpoles during the wet season (here dry). Bottom: ventral and lateral view of AF3422_A at Gosner stage 30, a close-up of the mouth, a picture of the specimen in situ within a small cavity in the lateritic crust indicated by an arrow, and the calling male nearby on lateritic crust." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4397451/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397445>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Two males (top) and one female (bottom) of the two species described herein, Anomaloglossus saramaka sp. nov. and A. vacheri sp. nov., along with one male of the three additional species of the A. stepheni group occurring in Suriname." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4397445/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4397447>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Views of dorsum, venter, left hand, left foot of the holotype of A. saramaka sp. nov. (left) and of the holotype of A. vacheri sp. nov. (right)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4397447/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

